"Change Set:		7732Exceptions-eem.12Exceptions-eem.12:First package of eight in closure compiler fixes 9/5/2009.Add reachedDefaultHandler to MessageNotUnderstood so that doesNotUnderstand: can support resume:."!Error subclass: #MessageNotUnderstood	instanceVariableNames: 'message receiver reachedDefaultHandler'	classVariableNames: ''	poolDictionaries: ''	category: 'Exceptions-Kernel'!!MessageNotUnderstood methodsFor: 'initialize-release' stamp: 'eem 12/19/2008 10:41'!initialize	super initialize.	reachedDefaultHandler := false! !!MessageNotUnderstood methodsFor: 'accessing' stamp: 'eem 12/19/2008 10:42'!reachedDefaultHandler	^reachedDefaultHandler! !!MessageNotUnderstood methodsFor: 'exceptionDescription' stamp: 'eem 12/19/2008 10:42'!defaultAction	reachedDefaultHandler := true.	super defaultAction! !